    <subfield code="a">26pp, LaTeX. Original title: "Finite dimensional quadratic Lie superalgebras"; abstract re-worded; text clarified; 3 references added; rearrangement of minor appendices into text; new subsection 4.2</subfield>
    <subfield code="9">arXiv</subfield>
